This adapter interfaces to the [http://www.yokogawa.co.jp Yokogawa] [http://www.yokogawa.co.jp/SCANNER/english/products/csu22e.html CSU22].  There is no additional software needed.  Connect the CSU22 to an available serial port on your computer (you will need a special adapter for this at the CSU22 end, I guess it comes with the confocal).  Serial port settings are standard (9600 baud).  You will need to defined the ''Hub'' device, and assign the right serial port to it. 

